========================================
COMMON ERRORS
========================================

1. redis-server not recognized
-> Redis not installed or PATH issue

2. ModuleNotFoundError
-> Run:
pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Dashboard fetch error
-> Backend not running or CORS issue

4. npm error
-> Run:
npm install


